TO GET YOUR TONGUE PIERCED.

04:30.871 --> 04:32.472
Isabel: MOM,
I WANT TO BE A MODEL.

04:32.506 --> 04:35.776
GET AN EATING DISORDER,
AND WE'LL TALK THEN.

04:35.809 --> 04:37.344
