05:54.254 --> 05:56.790
CHEAP‐ASS CORPORATE
COCKSUCKING COCKS!

05:56.823 --> 05:58.792
SIR, PLEASE.
I KIND OF LIKE YOU.

05:58.825 --> 06:00.961
