EXPENSE ACCOUNTS!

06:05.065 --> 06:07.201
FUCK ALL OF YOU!
FUCK ALL OF YOU!

06:07.234 --> 06:08.602
SIR!
YOU, TOO! YOU, TOO!

06:08.635 --> 06:10.904
