OVER THE PHONE TODAY,

07:05.292 --> 07:07.294
AND I'M HERE
TO PAY THE DEPOSIT IN CASH.

07:07.327 --> 07:09.530
DRIVER'S LICENSE
AND SOCIAL, PLEASE?

07:14.368 --> 07:15.569
