THE "OPRAH" CRACK.

07:55.242 --> 07:56.877
JUST GIVE ME POWER,
AND WE'LL CALL IT EVEN.

07:56.910 --> 08:02.449
YES, MRS. LaPLANTE.
NO PROBLEM.

08:04.351 --> 08:06.119
