11:17.010 --> 11:19.179
AND THE EQUIPMENT THAT I GOT
IS PRETTY SOPHISTICATED.

11:19.213 --> 11:21.915
JUST HOW SOPHISTICATED
ARE WE TALKING ABOUT?

11:21.949 --> 11:23.217
I'M TALKING
ABOUT TOP‐OF‐THE‐LINE.

11:23.250 --> 11:27.187
NONE OF THIS CHEAP, PASSIVE,
WICK SYSTEM BULLSHIT.

11:27.221 --> 11:30.023
IS THIS YOUR WAY OF TELLING ME
YOU'VE GONE OVER BUDGET?

11:30.057 --> 11:31.625
LET'S NOT GET HUNG UP
ON COST.

11:31.658 --> 11:34.862
MY PROJECTIONS SAY
WE'RE GONNA BE GENERATING
A MILLION‐PLUS IN REVENUE.

11:34.895 --> 11:36.063
NUMBERS.

11:36.096 --> 11:38.465
20 METAL HALIDE HORTILUX BULBS
AT $2,000 A POP.

11:38.498 --> 11:40.234
WE LOOKING AT MULTIPLE
100‐GALLON RESERVOIRS.

11:40.267 --> 11:41.935
[ BOTTLE RESONATING ]
[ LAUGHS ]

11:41.969 --> 11:43.670
PUMPS, 10 WALL FANS.

11:43.704 --> 11:44.838
WHAT ‐‐ 10% OVER?

11:44.872 --> 11:46.406
BABY, THIS IS MY VISION,
ALL RIGHT?

11:46.440 --> 11:48.141
AND WHEN I DO SOMETHING,
I DO IT RIGHT.

11:48.175 --> 11:50.544
NOTHING HALF‐ASSED ‐‐
I MEAN, WE GOT THE CASH, RIGHT?

11:50.577 --> 11:51.778
WHAT IF WE DON'T?

11:51.812 --> 11:54.281
DO YOU HAVE THE CASH?

11:54.314 --> 11:56.049
NO.

11:56.950 --> 11:59.119
LACY LaPLANTE MIGHT.

11:59.152 --> 12:01.655
WHY DO YOU BE PLAYING WITH ME
LIKE THIS?

12:01.688 --> 12:02.823
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

12:02.856 --> 12:04.691
SO, WHO'S THAT ‐‐
DIRECTV?

12:04.725 --> 12:06.827
PROBABLY.

12:06.860 --> 12:08.862
JESUS CHRIST!

12:08.896 --> 12:10.697
OH, IT'S JUST DEAN.

12:25.646 --> 12:26.780
YOU OKAY?

12:26.813 --> 12:29.249
GUESS WE SQUARE NOW.

12:29.283 --> 12:32.686
HEY, UM, HOW COME DEAN
DOESN'T HAVE TO CLEAN?

12:37.758 --> 12:39.760
[ SNORING ]

12:48.869 --> 12:50.671
[ INHALES SHARPLY, GROANS ]

12:50.704 --> 12:51.939
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

12:51.972 --> 12:54.107
EVERYONE IN MY GRADE
HAS ALREADY GOTTEN A HAND JOB.

12:54.141 --> 12:56.810
CONGRATS, LITTLE STUD.
HOW WAS IT?

12:56.844 --> 12:58.946
NO. EVERYONE BUT ME.

12:58.979 --> 13:02.049
AND NOW
THEY'RE MAKING FUN OF ME.

13:03.817 --> 13:05.085
FUCK 'EM.

13:05.118 --> 13:06.520
WHEN YOU WIN
THE PULITZER PRIZE,

13:06.553 --> 13:08.555
YOU KNOW HOW MUCH PUSSY
YOU'RE GONNA GET?

13:08.589 --> 13:12.159
I CAN'T WAIT THAT LONG.
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

13:14.027 --> 13:17.731
[ SIGHS ] WELL, THAT'S
EASY ENOUGH, YOUNG MAN.

13:17.764 --> 13:18.932
HUH?

13:18.966 --> 13:21.001
DON'T EVER SAY
I'M NOT A GOOD UNCLE.

13:26.940 --> 13:29.476
MIMOSA, MY DARLING?

13:29.510 --> 13:31.512
ISN'T IT A LITTLE EARLY
TO BE DRINKING,

13:31.545 --> 13:32.913
EVEN FOR YOU, CELIA?

13:32.946 --> 13:35.682
BIG DAY TODAY?

13:35.716 --> 13:36.850
OH, YEAH, YEAH.

13:36.884 --> 13:42.356
I HAVE TO TAKE DEPOSITIONS.
HUGE CASE.

13:42.389 --> 13:44.224
YEAH, OUR, UH...

13:44.258 --> 13:46.126
CLIENT WANTS TO SUE
THE CITY.

13:46.159 --> 13:48.262
[ CONTINUES TALKING ]

13:48.295 --> 13:49.062
[ BEEP ]

13:49.096 --> 13:50.464
Jack:
Dean, it's Jack.

13:50.497 --> 13:52.966
Sorry about
what happened today, buddy.

13:53.000 --> 13:55.002
If you need a recommendation,
let me know.

13:55.035 --> 13:57.871
[ ANSWERING MACHINE BEEPS ]

13:57.905 --> 14:00.507
Carla:
Hi, Mr. Hodes. It's Carla.

14:00.541 --> 14:03.377
I spoke to Blue Cross,
and you're eligible

14:03.410 --> 14:05.579
for this thing called C.O.B.R.A.
continuation coverage.

14:05.612 --> 14:07.314
And I'm not supposed
to be talking to you

14:07.347 --> 14:09.216
from here anymore, so call
my cellphone ‐‐ goodbye.

14:09.249 --> 14:12.452
[ ANSWERING MACHINE BEEPS ]

14:18.225 --> 14:22.763
I WAS THE ONE WHO RECOMMENDED
THAT THEY DOWNSIZE.

14:24.431 --> 14:27.034
I DEDICATED MY LIFE
TO THAT FIRM.

14:29.236 --> 14:32.139
HOW COULD YOU DO THIS
TO ME?

14:35.709 --> 14:38.145
OH, HE HASN'T
EVEN CALLED YET.

14:38.178 --> 14:41.849
OH, LOVE HAS FOUND
HEYLIA JAMES.

14:41.882 --> 14:43.517
[ SCOFFS ]
GIRL, YOU BETTER STOP.

14:43.550 --> 14:46.086
JUST 'CAUSE YOU AIN'T GOT
NOBODY IN YOUR BUSINESS

14:46.119 --> 14:47.888
DON'T MEAN YOU CAN BE
ALL UP IN MINE.

14:47.921 --> 14:49.289
DID HE SAY
HE WAS GONNA CALL?

14:49.323 --> 14:51.925
I SAID, "CALL ME," AND HE SAID,
"I DON'T HAVE YOUR NUMBER."

14:51.959 --> 14:54.795
SO I SAID, "I'M LISTED" ‐‐
MY HOME PHONE, ANYWAY.

14:54.828 --> 14:56.663
HAVEN'T LEFT THE HOUSE
IN TWO DAYS.

14:56.697 --> 14:57.698
[ LAUGHS ]

14:57.731 --> 14:59.466
HOW FUCKING PATHETIC
IS THAT?

14:59.499 --> 15:00.934
IT'S CUTE.

15:00.968 --> 15:02.236
IF HE WEREN'T HOPING

15:02.269 --> 15:04.304
FOR THE GLOBAL DESTRUCTION
OF THE WHITE RACE,

15:04.338 --> 15:06.340
I MIGHT REALLY BE ROOTING
FOR YOU TWO.

15:06.373 --> 15:10.110
HE DON'T MEAN THAT SHIT.
MAYBE HE DO.

15:10.143 --> 15:11.778
OH, I JUST LIKE HIM.

15:11.812 --> 15:14.848
SOMETIMES YOU FALL
FOR THE WRONG PEOPLE.

15:14.882 --> 15:17.217
SOMETHING
ABOUT THE WAY THEY SMELL

15:17.251 --> 15:20.721
OR SMILE OR CARRY
LITTLE PACKS

15:20.754 --> 15:22.523
OF TISSUES
IN THEIR POCKETS.

15:22.556 --> 15:24.958
MAYBE YOU DO GOT SOMEBODY
IN YOUR BUSINESS.

15:24.992 --> 15:27.861
YEAH, HE'S IN HIS 60's,
AND HE RIDES A SEGWAY,

15:27.895 --> 15:29.162
BUT THERE'S SOMETHING
ABOUT HIM.

15:29.196 --> 15:30.998
WHAT THE FUCK'S A SEGWAY?

15:31.031 --> 15:34.535
OH [LAUGHS] IT'S A THING
WITH TWO WHEELS

15:34.568 --> 15:36.303
THAT RICH WHITE PEOPLE
RIDE.

15:36.336 --> 15:39.740
WELL, AIN'T THE LUCKY STAR
SHINING ON YOUR LADY PARTS.

15:39.773 --> 15:41.141
EVEN IF I BREAK
MY STALLION,

15:41.175 --> 15:44.745
I AIN'T GETTING BOO
FOR ALLAH KNOWS HOW LONG.

15:44.778 --> 15:49.283
STILL, GIVES YOU A REASON
TO GET DRESSED IN THE MORNING.

15:51.818 --> 15:53.921
WHAT IF SHE DOESN'T LIKE ME?

15:53.954 --> 15:57.591
$80 AND A GENEROUS TIP
SAYS SHE WILL.

15:57.624 --> 15:59.026
NOW, KEEP YOUR MOUTH SHUT.

15:59.059 --> 16:02.729
CONSIDER THIS
AN EARLY BIRTHDAY PRESENT.

16:02.763 --> 16:04.064
ARE YOU GETTING ONE, TOO?

16:04.097 --> 16:06.633
[ LAUGHS ]
I GOT A DATE IN A FEW HOURS.

16:06.667 --> 16:08.135
OF COURSE
I'M GETTING ONE.

16:08.168 --> 16:11.205
NO WAY TO STAY COOL
IF YOU'RE BACKED UP.

16:12.673 --> 16:15.342
NICE WEDDING BAND.

16:19.012 --> 16:20.614
WHO NEXT?

16:22.182 --> 16:23.450
HI.

16:23.483 --> 16:25.819
MY LITTLE BUDDY OVER HERE
IS A FIRST‐TIMER.

16:25.853 --> 16:28.388
HE'S DONE THE SELF‐SERVE,
BUT HE'S LOOKING FOR A FULL.

16:28.422 --> 16:30.057
DO YOU HAVE
ANY STUDENT DISCOUNTS?

16:30.090 --> 16:32.759
YOU GO AWAY!
INAPPROPRIATE.

16:32.793 --> 16:34.728
INAPPROPRIATE BEHAVIOR.

16:34.761 --> 16:36.430
IS THIS
A NEGOTIATING PLOY?

16:36.463 --> 16:38.198
YOU DON'T BRING A LITTLE BOY
IN HERE.

16:38.232 --> 16:39.666
WHAT?
HIS MONEY'S NOT GREEN?

16:39.700 --> 16:41.835
COME ON. HE'S BEEN SAVING
HIS ALLOWANCE FOR WEEKS.

16:41.869 --> 16:44.371
YOU I DO.
LITTLE BOY, NO.

16:44.404 --> 16:46.440
WHERE'S RIA?

16:46.473 --> 16:47.908
RIA?

16:47.941 --> 16:48.909
Ria: WHAT?

16:48.942 --> 16:51.345
ANDREW.

16:51.378 --> 16:53.914
IT'S SO NICE TO SEE YOU.
IT'S BEEN A WHILE.

16:53.947 --> 16:55.349
YOU HAVE A DATE TONIGHT?

16:55.382 --> 16:58.785
WOULD YOU TELL MISS SAIGON
WE'RE HERE FOR BUSINESS?

16:58.819 --> 17:02.089
HE WANT A HAPPY FINISH
FOR A LITTLE BOY.

17:02.122 --> 17:03.423
INAPPROPRIATE.

17:03.457 --> 17:06.693
HE IS 18 WITH
A GLANDULAR PROBLEM, RIGHT?

17:06.727 --> 17:09.162
OF COURSE.
HE LITTLE BOY.

17:09.196 --> 17:11.698
IF SHE WON'T DO IT,
WHAT CAN I DO?

17:11.732 --> 17:12.966
ARTHRITIS.

17:13.000 --> 17:14.101
WELL, THERE'S ‐‐

17:14.134 --> 17:16.670
AND GINGIVITIS.

17:19.540 --> 17:21.742
AH, SORRY, LITTLE BUDDY.

17:21.775 --> 17:23.810
[ SOBBING ]

17:23.844 --> 17:26.980
OH, NO, DON'T CRY.

17:28.348 --> 17:29.983
DON'T CRY.

17:30.017 --> 17:32.085
HEY. HA, HA!

17:32.119 --> 17:34.555
[ SOBBING CONTINUES ]

17:34.588 --> 17:35.722
OKAY.

17:35.756 --> 17:37.024
COME ON.

17:44.765 --> 17:49.002
NICE MOVE
WITH THE TEARS, KID.

17:53.073 --> 17:55.309
GOING TO MEGAN'S.

17:55.342 --> 17:58.278
OF COURSE.

17:58.312 --> 18:01.348
LUPITA, I'M SORRY I TOOK
ALL YOUR SUPPLIES.

18:01.381 --> 18:02.683
YOU DID?

18:02.716 --> 18:04.985
I MEAN, YOU SHOULD ASK.

18:05.018 --> 18:06.687
I GET NOTHING DONE.

18:06.720 --> 18:08.121
WHAT DID YOU CLEAN?

18:08.155 --> 18:11.325
A HOMELESS SHELTER.
MADE ME FEEL GOOD.

18:11.358 --> 18:14.561
YOU KNOW, YOU CAN CLEAN
THE WHOLE HOUSE.

18:14.595 --> 18:15.729
MAKE YOU FEEL GREAT.

18:15.762 --> 18:18.732
HMM. I WOULDN'T WANT
TO TAKE THAT AWAY FROM YOU.

18:20.701 --> 18:21.869
ANDREW.

18:21.902 --> 18:23.270
WHERE WERE YOU?

18:23.303 --> 18:26.740
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO HELP ME
CLEAN...AT THE HOMELESS SHELTER.

18:26.773 --> 18:28.842
OH, YEAH,
THE HOMELESS SHELTER.

18:28.876 --> 18:31.378
WELL, I'VE BEEN DOING
MY OWN GOOD WORK.

18:32.779 --> 18:34.047
I NEED TO TAKE A NAP.

18:34.081 --> 18:36.083
SHANE,
WHAT ABOUT MOVIE NIGHT?

18:36.116 --> 18:38.585
I'M TIRED, MOM.

18:38.619 --> 18:40.754
SWEET DREAMS!

18:40.787 --> 18:43.991
I'VE BEEN STOOD UP.

18:44.024 --> 18:46.426
WELL, I GOT TO GET READY
FOR A DATE,

18:46.460 --> 18:49.229
SO CATCH YOU LATER,
MISS LONELY HEARTS.

18:54.034 --> 18:55.869
[ Phone ringing ]

18:55.903 --> 18:56.870
Hello?

18:56.904 --> 18:57.938
IT'S ME.

18:57.971 --> 19:00.240
HEY, YOU STILL WANT TO GO OUT
TONIGHT?

19:00.274 --> 19:02.409
MAYBE I'M NOT AVAILABLE
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE.

19:02.442 --> 19:04.011
ARE YOU?

19:04.044 --> 19:05.746
I COULD GO FOR A STEAK.

19:05.779 --> 19:08.282
AH, FOOD'S BORING.

19:08.315 --> 19:11.118
LET'S DO SOMETHING EXCITING.

19:23.931 --> 19:26.066
ARE YOU SURE
YOU'VE NEVER DONE THIS?

19:26.099 --> 19:27.801
YOU'RE A GOOD TEACHER.

19:27.835 --> 19:28.869
18 YEARS ON THE JOB.

19:28.902 --> 19:31.438
YOU EVER KILLED ANYBODY?

19:31.471 --> 19:33.373
18 YEARS ON THE JOB.

19:38.445 --> 19:42.716
WHAT'S TO STOP YOU
OR ME OR THEM

19:42.749 --> 19:44.785
FROM JUST
BLOWING SOMEBODY AWAY?

19:44.818 --> 19:47.554
DEATH ROW.

19:47.588 --> 19:48.956
OKAY.

19:48.989 --> 19:51.692
YOUR TURN.

19:51.725 --> 19:52.993
IT'S OKAY.

20:00.901 --> 20:01.969
[ THUDS ]

20:02.002 --> 20:03.270
ONE MORE?

20:03.303 --> 20:07.107
YOU HAVE, UM,
AMAZING SHOULDERS.

20:07.140 --> 20:09.009
NO, THEY'RE TARNISHED.

20:09.042 --> 20:12.079
LOOK ‐‐ BULLET WOUND
FROM THE ARMY.

20:12.112 --> 20:13.814
YOU SAW BATTLE?

20:13.847 --> 20:15.282
ISRAELI MEN ARE VERY MACHO.

20:15.315 --> 20:19.219
EVERYTHING IS ALL FINE WHEN YOU
BRING ANOTHER WOMAN INTO BED,

20:19.253 --> 20:21.955
BUT YOU BRING ANOTHER MAN,
AND THEY GO CRAZY.

20:21.989 --> 20:24.091
SO HE SHOT YOU?

20:24.124 --> 20:25.759
TO BE HONEST,
IF HE HADN'T,

20:25.792 --> 20:28.095
I WOULD HAVE THOUGHT
HE WAS A FAGGOT.

20:28.929 --> 20:31.064
AND THE SEX WAS GREAT
THAT NIGHT.

20:31.098 --> 20:33.834
THE PAIN
AND THE PLEASURE ‐‐

20:33.867 --> 20:36.203
MMM, VERY EXCITING.

20:36.236 --> 20:37.905
MMM!

20:37.938 --> 20:39.673
L'CHAYIM.

20:39.706 --> 20:41.775
MM‐HMM.

20:41.808 --> 20:43.744
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

20:45.913 --> 20:47.080
HELLO?

20:47.114 --> 20:49.416
HEYLIA? THIS IS JOSEPH.

20:49.449 --> 20:52.286
JOSEPH?

20:52.319 --> 20:54.388
JOSEPH.

20:54.421 --> 20:55.889
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

20:55.923 --> 20:57.391
SO, UM, HOW ARE YOU?

20:57.424 --> 21:00.527
WELL, I'M FEELING
SOMEWHAT CONFLICTED, HEYLIA.

21:00.561 --> 21:01.595
AS A FOLLOWER OF ISLAM,

21:01.628 --> 21:04.398
ONE OF THE EVILS
WE MUST BE WATCHFUL FOR

21:04.431 --> 21:08.168
IS THE ENTICING BEAUTY
OF WOMEN.

21:08.202 --> 21:10.971
Yet I ‐‐ I'd very much like
to see you.

21:11.004 --> 21:12.806
THAT'S A COMPLIMENT, RIGHT?

21:12.840 --> 21:14.341
ARE YOU AVAILABLE
FOR MARRIAGE?

21:14.374 --> 21:15.776
EXCUSE ME?

21:15.809 --> 21:18.078
DID YOU JUST PROPOSE?

21:18.111 --> 21:21.615
DAMN, YOU DON'T WASTE NO TIME,
FARRAKHAN.

21:21.648 --> 21:24.985
OH, NO, NO.
I'M SORRY IF YOU MISUNDERSTOOD.

21:25.018 --> 21:26.520
I WAS JUST INQUIRING

21:26.553 --> 21:29.356
IF YOU WERE AVAILABLE
FOR MARRIAGE DOWN THE LINE.

21:29.389 --> 21:32.926
Right now, I wish us
to get better acquainted.

21:32.960 --> 21:34.828
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:34.862 --> 21:38.565
I JUST LOVE THE WAY YOU TALK.

21:38.599 --> 21:40.000
YOU WANT TO DATE ME, RIGHT?

21:40.033 --> 21:41.768
Woman: LOOK, I'VE BEEN WAITING
HERE FOR TWO HOURS.

21:41.802 --> 21:43.504
EXCUSE ME JUST A MINUTE,
HEYLIA.

21:45.138 --> 21:47.808
I UNDERSTAND
YOUR FRUSTRATION, MA'AM,

21:47.841 --> 21:49.810
AND WE WILL FIND YOUR BAGS.

21:49.843 --> 21:52.679
I'M DOING MY BEST.

21:52.713 --> 21:54.348
Devil bitch.

21:54.381 --> 21:58.285
HEYLIA, I'M AFRAID
ANYTHING BEYOND PHONE CALLS

21:58.318 --> 22:01.288
WOULD BE UNWISE
AT THIS JUNCTURE.

22:01.321 --> 22:04.124
THE TEMPTATION
WOULD BE TOO GREAT.

22:04.157 --> 22:08.495
HOW LONG IT GONNA TAKE UNTIL YOU
GET UNWISE, 'CAUSE, WELL,

22:08.529 --> 22:11.865
NO DISRESPECT TO MUHAMMAD,
BUT I THINK YOU'RE DAMN FINE,

22:11.899 --> 22:13.800
AND I WANT TO SEE YOU
FACE‐TO‐FACE.

22:13.834 --> 22:15.802
I'LL SEE YOU IN 40 MINUTES.

22:15.836 --> 22:19.406
THE WHITE ZONE IS FOR IMMEDIATE
<i>LOADING AND UNLOADING...</i>

22:19.439 --> 22:21.642
[ LAUGHTER ]

22:21.675 --> 22:23.210
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

22:23.243 --> 22:26.013
OH, I THOUGHT WE
WERE HITTING IT OFF.

22:26.046 --> 22:28.215
YEAH, WE ARE.

22:28.248 --> 22:30.584
GOOD.

22:30.617 --> 22:33.020
UH...OH, I'M SORRY.

22:33.053 --> 22:36.623
IT'S TOO SOON
SINCE YOUR LOVER DIED.

22:36.657 --> 22:38.792
NO, I'VE BEEN WITH MANY MEN.

22:38.825 --> 22:40.794
HELPS TO GET OVER THINGS.

22:40.827 --> 22:42.563
MM‐HMM. GOOD.

22:42.596 --> 22:45.766
AM I GETTING
MIXED MESSAGES HERE OR...

22:45.799 --> 22:49.269
LOOK, YOU'RE ADORABLE...

22:49.303 --> 22:53.740
BUT I'M NOT ATTRACTED
TO YOU.

22:53.774 --> 22:54.842
SORRY.

22:54.875 --> 22:56.810
ARE YOU A CHUBBY CHASER
OR SOMETHING?

22:56.844 --> 22:59.513
NO, YOU JUST ‐‐

22:59.546 --> 23:01.748
I LIKE A MAN,

23:01.782 --> 23:03.750
SOMEONE BIG AND STRONG,

23:03.784 --> 23:06.253
SOMEONE WHO CAN GROW A BEARD.

23:06.286 --> 23:09.723
YOU'RE PRETTY, AND I COULD
FLIP YOU LIKE A PANCAKE.

23:09.756 --> 23:11.091
YOU'D ASK PERMISSION

23:11.124 --> 23:13.627
INSTEAD OF JUST SLAMMING ME
UP AGAINST A WALL

23:13.660 --> 23:16.430
AND FUCKING ME UNTIL I CUM
LIKE A VOLCANO.

23:16.463 --> 23:20.834
BUT WE CAN STILL BE FRIENDS,
RIGHT?

23:20.868 --> 23:23.170
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

23:23.203 --> 23:27.841
I WANT TO TRY THE GLOCK NEXT,
OR MAYBE THE MAGNUM.

23:27.875 --> 23:30.811
EASY THERE, COWGIRL.
MAYBE NEXT TIME.

23:30.844 --> 23:32.779
WE'RE DONE?

23:32.813 --> 23:34.715
I'VE GOT A LONG DRIVE
TO PACIFIC BEACH,

23:34.748 --> 23:37.684
AND IT TAKES ME HOURS TO
STERILIZE MY PIERCING NEEDLES.

23:37.718 --> 23:39.753
SORRY.

23:39.786 --> 23:42.022
DO YOU LIKE
GOING UNDERCOVER?

23:42.055 --> 23:44.291
WITH YOU I DO.

23:44.324 --> 23:47.828
OH, COME ON.
IT'S EXCITING, ISN'T IT?

23:47.861 --> 23:49.796
UNTIL YOU GET SHOT
IN THE ASS

23:49.830 --> 23:52.833
BY A METH FREAK
WITH A NAIL GUN.

23:52.866 --> 23:55.135
YEAH, IT'S EXCITING.

23:57.671 --> 23:59.606
BYE.

24:04.678 --> 24:08.882
CAN I TRY THE SHINY ONE
WITH THE PRETTY, PEARLY GRIP.

24:08.916 --> 24:10.584
SORRY, WE'RE CLOSING
IN 10 MINUTES.

24:10.617 --> 24:13.420
YOU DON'T HAVE TO GO HOME,
BUT YOU CAN'T SHOOT HERE.

24:13.453 --> 24:14.521
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:14.555 --> 24:18.859
OH, HERE'S YOUR LICENSE,
MS. LaPLANTE.

24:18.892 --> 24:19.927
IT'S LACY.

24:19.960 --> 24:22.729
MY MOTHER IS MS. LaPLANTE.

24:33.507 --> 24:35.209
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

24:36.343 --> 24:38.145
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
BACK HERE?

24:38.178 --> 24:41.481
HOW OFTEN DO YOU GET TO SEE
A GROW HOUSE BEING BUILT?

24:41.515 --> 24:43.784
WHOA, HOLD, BABY.
CLOSE YOUR EYES.

24:43.817 --> 24:45.252
CLOSE YOUR EYES.

24:45.285 --> 24:46.119
SHUT UP.

24:46.153 --> 24:48.889
I'M SERIOUS. COME ON.
CLOSE YOUR EYES.

24:48.922 --> 24:50.324
STEP IN.

24:52.059 --> 24:57.698
NOW, I WANT YOU TO PICTURE
A BRIGHT, BRIGHT ROOM

24:57.731 --> 25:00.534
FILLED WITH BEAUTIFUL,
