25:39.072 --> 25:42.609
THANK YOU, VICTOR.

25:42.643 --> 25:44.578
THEY'RE REAL, YOU KNOW.

25:44.611 --> 25:46.413
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

25:46.446 --> 25:48.448
WHO THE HELL IS THAT?

26:02.863 --> 26:04.498
CAN I HELP YOU?

26:04.531 --> 26:06.900
