26:06.934 --> 26:07.935
WHAT IS IT?

26:07.968 --> 26:09.303
BAKLAVA.

26:09.336 --> 26:10.337
WHAT FOR?

26:10.370 --> 26:13.207
YOU ARE NEW
TO THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

26:13.240 --> 26:15.142
