OR A FLAT‐SCREEN TV."

26:40.834 --> 26:42.769
BUT, NO.

26:42.803 --> 26:45.873
IT WAS ALL BOXES,

26:45.906 --> 26:48.809
AND I KNOW THESE BOXES.

26:48.842 --> 26:51.812
THESE ARE VICTOR'S BOXES.

26:51.845 --> 26:55.782
