ABOUT HIS BUSINESS.

27:50.804 --> 27:51.772
WE GOT TO MOVE.

27:51.805 --> 27:54.541
THIS IS AMERICA.

27:54.575 --> 27:56.610
WE CAN ALL DO BUSINESS.

27:56.643 --> 27:59.112
WE'LL SEND HIM COOKIES.
SCARE THE SHIT OUT OF HIM.

27:59.146 --> 28:01.815
