28:01.849 --> 28:03.784
WE HAVE PROBLEMS.

28:03.817 --> 28:06.086
THERE'S ALWAYS PROBLEMS.

28:06.119 --> 28:08.121
THERE'S ALWAYS SOLUTIONS.

28:09.056 --> 28:10.858
KEEP GOING, FELLAS.

28:10.891 --> 28:11.859
ARE YOU SURE?

28:11.892 --> 28:13.560
I'M SURE.

28:13.594 --> 28:14.628
FINE.

28:14.661 --> 28:19.933
