FOR A SECOND, PLEASE?

28:19.967 --> 28:21.268
SHE'S GOT TO GO HOME.

28:21.301 --> 28:23.437
YOU CAN TALK TO HER TOMORROW.

28:24.738 --> 28:28.442
FINISH.

28:44.725 --> 28:46.760
